values:
Last nite Tari slept over her friends house, I missed her.

Last nite she had to empty my tank all the way because some naughty mosquitos laid eggs in my tank, and their are still babies in there, they taist good. 

she is nervous about these big new turtles she is getting, altho she told me she wanted babies, these 2 need a good home.
today I let Tari take pictures of me, here are a few

Today Tari went out to get me food today, she bought me more of the red floating balls that I like and 10 rosy red minnows... they were good. I showed my apprication by going into a feeding frenzy... They are not as large as the goldfish she used to give me, but she says these are healthier. She is nervous about something... she has been cleaning a lot. she messed up our room very badly, and one of her frogs died... I think she cried a bit, she wanted them to have babies to feed to me

Tari has been trying to to take pictures of me lately, but I have not been a good turtle. She is working hard on the plans for my enclouser. people keep giving me new ideas... I am thinking of going allong with them. 2 feet tall will be fine for the enclouser I think. but I am afaraid of growing out of it. wanna see more pictures of me?

Hello all. I am Fyre, a Female common snapping turtle. I belong to Xafthertherain we live togather in her parents attic with 2 frogs, and a few fish tanks. Shh dont tell anyone but she soon plans to repace the fish with turtles or all different types, since I am very anti social. I am also very messy. I am getting old (one year and 4 months allready and very large, even if i am in a tank i out grew at birth) I may have to look for a new home soon if Rain can't get her parents to let her house me in the yard. well thats all for my first entry. Laters all. I have to make a cool icon!
